title: BeatBox

creator: PipeFlare Games
descriptionHtml:
Experience the ultimate thrill in Beatbox! Smash through endless bricks, obstacles, unlock a myriad of skins, and conquer challenges. Compete on the leaderboard for supremacy in this supercharged arcade adventure. Brace yourself for a fast-paced journey where precision meets excitement. How many bricks can you break? Find out as you navigate through super crazy obstacles, customize your gameplay with a variety of skins, and take on challenging missions. Aim, shoot, and rise to the top of the leaderboard in this addictive and visually stunning brick-breaking extravaganza!

How To Play:
- The ball shoots to wherever you touch on the screen
- Clear each stage by removing bricks on the board
- Break the bricks and never let them hit the bottom
- Find great positions and angles to destroy to most bricks

Features:
- Free To Play
- Unlimited Stages
- Many Types Of Balls
- Easy To Play
- Kills Time
- Tablet Supported
- Facebook/Twitter/Gmail Login
descriptionShort: Break bricks, score points – classic arcade fun in Brick Breaker!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Fix bugs
- Added Free Trial
- Added Weekly, Monthly Hardcore Supporter
- Added Remove Ads Package
